STATE of Iowa, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Monte Allen APFEL, Defendant-Appellant. No. 18-0440 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed January 9, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

Monte Apfel challenges his convictions of possession of methamphetamine with intent to deliver, possession of marijuana, possession of diazepam, unlawful possession of prescription drugs, and drug tax stamp violation. AFFIRMED.

AFFIRMED.
